---
import EmailCapture from '../EmailCapture.astro';
---

  <section class="hero-mini">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 data-en="Run For Denver" data-es="Postúlate por Denver">Run For Denver</h1>
      <p data-en="We're building a movement for economic justice in Denver. We have the platform, the volunteers, and the energy. We need a candidate who will fight for it." data-es="Estamos construyendo un movimiento por la justicia económica en Denver. Tenemos la plataforma, los voluntarios y la energía. Necesitamos un candidato que luche por esto.">
        We're building a movement for economic justice in Denver. We have the platform,
        the volunteers, and the energy. We need a candidate who will fight for it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <h2 data-en="What We're Looking For" data-es="Lo Que Buscamos">What We're Looking For</h2>

      <div class="criteria-grid">
        <div class="criteria-card">
          <h3 data-en="Working Class Roots" data-es="Raíces de Clase Trabajadora">Working Class Roots</h3>
          <p data-en="Someone who knows what it's like to worry about rent, to choose between groceries and medicine. Not another wealthy candidate who 'cares about the poor' - someone who has lived it." data-es="Alguien que sepa lo que es preocuparse por el alquiler, elegir entre comida y medicina. No otro candidato rico que 'se preocupa por los pobres' - alguien que lo ha vivido.">
            Someone who knows what it's like to worry about rent, to choose between groceries and medicine. Not another wealthy candidate who "cares about the poor" - someone who has lived it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="criteria-card">
          <h3 data-en="Movement Builder" data-es="Constructor de Movimientos">Movement Builder</h3>
          <p data-en="Demonstrated commitment to housing justice, labor rights, or community organizing. We want someone who has been in the fight, not someone who just discovered inequality during campaign season." data-es="Compromiso demostrado con la justicia de vivienda, derechos laborales u organización comunitaria. Queremos a alguien que ha estado en la lucha, no alguien que descubrió la desigualdad durante la temporada de campaña.">
            Demonstrated commitment to housing justice, labor rights, or community organizing. We want someone who has been in the fight, not someone who just discovered inequality during campaign season.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="criteria-card">
          <h3 data-en="People-Funded Only" data-es="Financiado Solo por el Pueblo">People-Funded Only</h3>
          <p data-en="Willing to reject all corporate PAC money. No developer donations. No landlord money. No corporate bundlers. Small-dollar grassroots fundraising only. The people who fund you are the people you serve." data-es="Dispuesto a rechazar todo dinero de PACs corporativos. Sin donaciones de desarrolladores. Sin dinero de propietarios. Sin intermediarios corporativos. Solo recaudación popular de pequeñas cantidades. La gente que te financia es la gente a la que sirves.">
            Willing to reject all corporate PAC money. No developer donations. No landlord money. No corporate bundlers. Small-dollar grassroots fundraising only. The people who fund you are the people you serve.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="criteria-card">
          <h3 data-en="Committed to the Platform" data-es="Comprometido con la Plataforma">Committed to the Platform</h3>
          <p data-en="Ready to champion our full platform: social housing, rent control, $25 minimum wage, one fair wage, universal right to counsel, and every other policy we've developed with community input." data-es="Listo para defender toda nuestra plataforma: vivienda social, control de alquileres, salario mínimo de $25, un salario justo, derecho universal a representación legal, y cada otra política que hemos desarrollado con aportes de la comunidad.">
            Ready to champion our full platform: social housing, rent control, $25 minimum wage, one fair wage, universal right to counsel, and every other policy we've developed with community input.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="criteria-card">
          <h3 data-en="Bilingual or Multilingual" data-es="Bilingüe o Multilingüe">Bilingual or Multilingual</h3>
          <p data-en="Denver's Latino community is 30%+ of the city. Ideally our candidate speaks Spanish, but at minimum must be committed to genuine representation - not tokenism - for all of Denver's communities." data-es="La comunidad latina de Denver es más del 30% de la ciudad. Idealmente nuestro candidato habla español, pero como mínimo debe estar comprometido con una representación genuina - no simbólica - para todas las comunidades de Denver.">
            Denver's Latino community is 30%+ of the city. Ideally our candidate speaks Spanish, but at minimum must be committed to genuine representation - not tokenism - for all of Denver's communities.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="criteria-card">
          <h3 data-en="Ready to Win" data-es="Listo para Ganar">Ready to Win</h3>
          <p data-en="Can commit to 2027 mayoral race OR 2025/2027 city council. Has the energy, resilience, and fire to run a grassroots campaign against better-funded establishment candidates. We have the infrastructure - you bring the fight." data-es="Puede comprometerse con la carrera por la alcaldía de 2027 O el concejo municipal de 2025/2027. Tiene la energía, resiliencia y fuego para ejecutar una campaña popular contra candidatos del establishment mejor financiados. Nosotros tenemos la infraestructura - tú traes la lucha.">
            Can commit to 2027 mayoral race OR 2025/2027 city council. Has the energy, resilience, and fire to run a grassroots campaign against better-funded establishment candidates. We have the infrastructure - you bring the fight.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="who-section">
        <h2 data-en="Who Should Apply" data-es="Quién Debe Postularse">Who Should Apply</h2>
        <ul>
          <li data-en="Tenant organizers and housing advocates" data-es="Organizadores de inquilinos y defensores de la vivienda">Tenant organizers and housing advocates</li>
          <li data-en="Union leaders - teachers, nurses, service workers" data-es="Líderes sindicales - maestros, enfermeros, trabajadores de servicios">Union leaders - teachers, nurses, service workers</li>
          <li data-en="Public defenders and tenant lawyers" data-es="Defensores públicos y abogados de inquilinos">Public defenders and tenant lawyers</li>
          <li data-en="Climate and environmental justice activists" data-es="Activistas de justicia climática y ambiental">Climate and environmental justice activists</li>
          <li data-en="Community organizers from DSA, Colorado People's Alliance, 9to5, and similar orgs" data-es="Organizadores comunitarios de DSA, Colorado People's Alliance, 9to5 y organizaciones similares">Community organizers from DSA, Colorado People's Alliance, 9to5, and similar orgs</li>
          <li data-en="Social workers, counselors, and care workers" data-es="Trabajadores sociales, consejeros y cuidadores">Social workers, counselors, and care workers</li>
          <li data-en="Local journalists who cover inequality" data-es="Periodistas locales que cubren la desigualdad">Local journalists who cover inequality</li>
          <li data-en="Anyone who has been failed by the system and wants to change it" data-es="Cualquiera que haya sido defraudado por el sistema y quiera cambiarlo">Anyone who has been failed by the system and wants to change it</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="apply-section">
        <h2 data-en="Ready to Run?" data-es="¿Listo para Postularte?">Ready to Run?</h2>
        <p data-en="Tell us about yourself. This isn't a formal application - it's the start of a conversation. We want to hear your story, your vision, and why you want to fight for Denver." data-es="Cuéntanos sobre ti. Esto no es una solicitud formal - es el inicio de una conversación. Queremos escuchar tu historia, tu visión y por qué quieres luchar por Denver.">
          Tell us about yourself. This isn't a formal application - it's the start of a conversation.
          We want to hear your story, your vision, and why you want to fight for Denver.
        </p>
        <a href="https://forms.gle/PPMqH22R6U3kUa796" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--primary btn--large" data-en="Tell Us About Yourself" data-es="Cuéntanos Sobre Ti">
          Tell Us About Yourself
        </a>
        <p class="apply-note" data-en="Or email us directly at info@denverforall.org" data-es="O escríbenos directamente a info@denverforall.org">
          Or email us directly at info@denverforall.org
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <EmailCapture />
    </div>
  </section>

<style>
  .hero-mini {
    padding: 4rem 0 3rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-mini h1 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-mini p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 700px;
  }

  .criteria-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .criteria-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .criteria-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .criteria-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .who-section {
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .who-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .who-section li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .who-section li::before {
    content: '\2192';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .apply-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .apply-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .apply-section p {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .apply-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-top: 1rem !important;
  }
</style>
